ğŸ§ª Retraining Models
To retrain:

Go to the "Retrain" tab.

Choose a folder of images and select the corresponding mask suffix (_cp_masks by default).

Select a pretrained .pth model as your base.

Start training â€” the model will be saved in the models/ subfolder.

